    "description": "本課程主要在於認識兒童常見的行為問題及障礙，並探討兒童行為問題的輔導策略及技巧，以增進對兒童行為及情緒問題之理解與處遇的專業知能。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.常見的兒童行為問題，以及輔導策略與技巧。<br>2.幫助兒童學習順從。<br>3.幫助兒童學習遵守規定。<br>4.增進兒童的社交行為技巧。<br>5.增進兒童的問題解決技巧。<br>6.增進兒童處理生氣的能力。<br>7.增進兒童管理自己學業的行為技巧。<br>8.增進兒童瞭解及表達感覺的能力。<br>9.幫助父母增進處理兒童行為問題的能力與技巧。<br>",
        "en": "1. Common problem with children’s behavior, and counseling strategies and techniques.<br>2. Help children learn to obey.<br>3. Help children to learn by following the rules.<br>4. Improve children's social behavior skills.<br>5. Improve children's problem-solving skills.<br>6. Improve children's ability to manage their anger.<br>7. Improve children's behavioral skills in managing their own studies.<br>8. Improve children's ability in both understanding and expressing feelings.<br>9. Help parents improve their ability and skills in dealing with children’s behavioral problems.<br>"
    },
